<p>This is how im serializing an object. How to I retrieve the xml string to replace the single quotes?    </p>  <pre><code>var settings = new XmlWriterSettings {OmitXmlDeclaration = true};              settings.Encoding = Encoding.ASCII;              var writer = XmlWriter.Create(writeStream, settings);              var serializer = new XmlSerializer(value.GetType());              var nameSpaces = new XmlSerializerNamespaces();              nameSpaces.Add(string.Empty, string.Empty);              serializer.Serialize(writer, value, nameSpaces); </code></pre>